This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on domain randomization, which is a technique used in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper deals with control and optimization, which are topics in systems and control theory, so cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely but still possible sub-category.
